{"inkVersion":21,"root":[[{"->":"chapter_1"},["done",{"#f":5,"#n":"g-0"}],null],"done",{"chapter_1":["^$DISABLE_ALL_ACTIONS ","#","^auto:true","/#","\n","^$SLEEP:1 ","#","^auto:true","/#","\n","^“TF4674 于甚高频频道 16 呼叫 X92HKM。收到请回答，完毕。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“X92HKM 抄收 TF4674 的信号。我看到光了！你真的是灯塔！” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_happy ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“什么叫真的是啦……这有什么好骗你的。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_smile ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_mi","/#","\n","^“可是海图上确实没有这样的标记，是不是因为废弃了很久了呢。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_default_2 ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do","/#","\n","^“对着一个正在亮着的灯塔说废弃什么的真是失礼啊……” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_awkward ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“那可真是对不起啦。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_smile ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do","/#","\n","^“完全没听出哪儿有对不起的意思了。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speechless_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“嘛嘛别介意。说回来，能帮我再问问海岸警卫队的情况？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_default_1","/#","\n","^“咦？你没有收到他们的通讯吗？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_confused_flip_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“没有喔。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_default_2","/#","\n","^“那确实有点奇怪……稍等，我试着联系一下。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_default ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^$SLEEP:0.5","\n","^“COAST GUARD, COAST GUARD, COAST GUARD. 这里是TF4674，灯塔「磷光」。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“收到来自科研船「薄明」的 MAYDAY 信号，呼号 X92HKM，方位北纬  66°35'26\"、西经 17°56'16\"。需求紧急援助。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“前系 MAYDAY RELAY 无应答。UTC 时间 1911，完毕。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_default ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^$SLEEP:1.5 ","#","^auto:true","/#","\n","^（无线电静默） ","#","^type:FullScreenText ","/#","#","^opacity:0.8","/#","\n","^“确实……太奇怪了。海岸警卫队居然毫无应答。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_thinking_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“啊，果然呢……” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_la ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_sad_1","/#","\n","^“果然？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_confused_flip_1  ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“毕竟是这个时代嘛。我还以为真的会有海岸警卫队之类的。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_smile","/#","\n","^“你说得就好像这个时代不应该有救援和海岸警卫队一样。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“难道应该有吗？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_default_2","/#","\n","^“……为什么你会觉得不应该有？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_confused_flip_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“因为，「大涨潮」过后，绝大部分邻近海岸线的城市已经全部被淹没了吧？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_default_1","/#","\n","^“人们为了重新回到正轨都已经倾尽全力了，哪还有余力还援助海上的船舶……” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_la ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_sad_1","/#","\n","^“等等等等，「大涨潮」是什么？城市被淹没？我怎么从来没有听说过这回事。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_surprised ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_mi","/#","\n","^“欸？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_shocked_1","/#","\n","^“欸？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_default ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“四个月前的海平面无预兆剧烈上涨，5% 的陆地被海洋淹没，约 15 亿人遇难或行踪不明，被摧毁的城市与基础设施更不必说……” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_default_1","/#","\n","^“这就是「大涨潮」。你们有别的称呼方法？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_sad_1","/#","\n","^“不……”  ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_surprised ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“那为什么你这么惊讶。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_default_2","/#","\n","^“因为我根本没有听说过它的发生，不如说我很确定它没有发生。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“为什么？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_default_1","/#","\n","^“如果真的海平面剧烈上涨了，那我就不会现在还在灯塔的底层通讯室里与你通话。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“我早就被淹死了。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speechless ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“……有道理喔！那难道是我记忆错乱了吗。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_shocked_2","/#","\n","^“别这么轻易就否定自己刚刚说过的话啊……！” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_awkward ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“因为你的理由很令人信服。就算你是一个在我的海图上没有标识的灯塔……” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_la ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_default_2","/#","\n","^“咦，没有标识的话……” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_serious","/#","\n","^“有头绪了？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_default  ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“我在找这张海图的制图日期。”","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_la ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_default_1","/#","\n","^“要么是因为这个海图制于你灯塔建成前，要么就是因为你灯塔废弃太久而不再标记……” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_serious","/#","\n","^“啊，找到了。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_default_1","/#","\n","^“是什么时候的？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_default ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“2075 年 3 月 28 日。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_default_2","/#","\n","^“啊？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_surprised ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_mi","/#","\n","^“2075 年 3 月 28 日？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_confused_flip_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“是的，是 7 喔不是 1 喔。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_smile","/#","\n","^“……那我觉得是后者了。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speechless_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“意思是说灯塔废弃太久吗？可是你不是自己都说还在维护？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_default_1","/#","\n","^“我确实还在维护它，但我不知道一百年后我还在不在维护它。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“一百年后……什么意思？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_default_2","/#","\n","^“我认为今天应该是 1982 年 1 月 23 日。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_default ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“……” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_shocked_3","/#","\n","^“1982 年？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_shocked_1","/#","\n","^“如果暂且不谈这个解释不了的时间差，很多事情就都说得通了。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“包括我为什么没有听说过「大涨潮」，也没有受到它的影响。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“以及你的呼号头为什么是一个被保留的呼号头。在 1982 年，X9 这个呼号头还没有被任何国家或组织使用。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“……但最大的问题就是，这是你的玩笑，还是确有其事？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_thinking_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“……” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_default_2","/#","\n","^“……原来是这样吗？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_default_1","/#","\n","^“……嗯？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_confused_0.5 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“我还在想为什么突然会有无线电应答，原来是我出现幻觉了啊……” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_sad_1","/#","\n","^“不要随便就把别人当作是你的幻觉啊。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_angry_2  ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“这倒是真的玩笑啦。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_smile","/#","\n","^“但我也希望我之前说的不是玩笑，以及我听到的不是玩笑。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_la ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_serious","/#","\n","^“如果你是一百年前的灯塔……那大概求救也无济于事。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_sad_1","/#","\n","^“对不起啊。突然有个莫名其妙的声音请求援救，还说自己来自未来什么的……” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_smile","/#","\n","^“……灯塔有义务答复并转发任何 MAYDAY 信号。现在的当务之急还是联系上海岸警卫队。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_look_upwards ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“不必了。就算联系上了，也是 1982 年的海岸警卫队吧？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_la ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_default_2","/#","\n","^“那也要试了才知道！” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_default ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_mi","/#","\n","^“不用试了。我这个时代本来就不存在什么海岸警卫队了。之前的呼叫不也一直没有收到回复吗。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_default_2","/#","\n","^“……” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speechless","/#","\n","^“……能与你说上话，我已经很满足了。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_la ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_smile","/#","\n","^“……” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speechless","/#","\n","^“……不。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_default ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“嗯？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_shocked_1","/#","\n","^“现在说放弃还太早。你刚刚说还能看到灯塔的光？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“嗯，怎么？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_default_2","/#","\n","^“那就说明灯塔里有人。虽然不知道这个人是我还是别人，不论如何，我有一个提案。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_look_upwards ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“我去开关航标灯。如果你看到的航标灯明灭与我一样，那就说明你看到的是来自我的光。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_default  ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_mi","/#","\n","^“……很有说服力。但为什么要验证这个？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_default_1","/#","\n","^“如果你看到的是我发出的光的话，那换句话说，你看到的是我所在的 1982 年的灯塔。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“如果你有需要的话，我起码能给你提供一些物资。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“那如果没有变呢？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_default_2","/#","\n","^“那也可以去灯塔求救，说不定灯塔里真的还有人。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_default ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“不管怎么样，都还没到放弃的时候。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_smile ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“……我明白了” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_default_1","/#","\n","^“我随时都可以开始喔。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_smile","/#","\n","^“不用给你留一些赶到甲板上的时间吗？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_default ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“我现在就在甲板上喔。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_default_1","/#","\n","^“啊？你把电台搬到甲板上了？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_surprised ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“不是啦。这是可移动手台，能把船上的电台作为中继器用，走到哪儿都可以和你通信。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_smile","/#","\n","^“要说的话，我现在就在看着灯塔喔？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:X92HKM ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re ","/#","#","^avatar:radio_happy","/#","\n","^“……真是方便啊，我开始相信你是 2075 年的人了。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_smile ",